11065.post_excerpt: Some of the unique features include images with overlapping social icons, featured posts with unique links and a special trip page layout designed to tell your story in an elegant way. The blog page is fullwidth with large featured images that work well for a travel blog. And the Noto Serif font choice fits really well with the overall design.
